    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Genitalia of Simmeiropsis algharbensis sp. n. 1. apical part of penis in dorsal view; 2. penis in lateral view; 3. genital armature of the internal sac; 4. spermatheca; 5. gonocoxites; 6. spiculum ventrale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219102/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219104>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 14. Habitus of Simmeiropsis algharbensis sp. n., 13. male; 14, female." ;
